Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:55.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(842,580)}高菲高伯
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.08,0:00:59.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能再来一份三倍高伯莓黎明吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.08,0:00:56.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can we get another
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.96,0:00:59.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Triple Gooberberry Sunrise over here?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.64,0:01:01.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三倍的可别不舍得拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:01.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And don't you skimp on the triple
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.77,0:01:03.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们的黎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:03.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your sun--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.93,0:01:05.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.93,0:01:05.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's starting
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.52,0:01:10.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要再来一份
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:10.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take another one
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.22,0:01:12.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这次经理加少点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.22,0:01:12.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This time with less manager
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.70,0:01:15.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位无论多大年纪的小朋友请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.70,0:01:15.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, children of all ages
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.30,0:01:16.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:16.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, hi
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.40,0:01:16.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:16.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.98,0:01:17.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱你  我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.98,0:01:17.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love you, I love you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.90,0:01:18.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多大都行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.90,0:01:18.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All ages
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.63,0:01:22.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请大家鳍声欢迎架子鼓能手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.63,0:01:22.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put your fins together for the cool cat on the drum kit
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.70,0:01:24.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邦戈熊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:24.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bongos Bear
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.22,0:01:29.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这只贝壳吹小号的节奏感特别强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.22,0:01:29.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On trumpet, this bivalve really swings
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.30,0:01:30.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蛤蜊克莱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:30.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clem Clam
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.37,0:01:33.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家认识他  大家爱他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:33.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know him, you love him
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.52,0:01:36.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,八个触手弹八十八个琴键
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:36.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eight tentacles on 88 keys
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.50,0:01:39.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就是摇滚普斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:39.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's Rock T. Puss
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.57,0:01:41.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是我们的乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:41.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's our combo
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.16,0:01:45.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鳍声有请高菲掌勺乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:45.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give it up for the Goofy Scoopers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:45.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(988,190)}高菲掌勺乐队
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.16,0:01:47.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一啊二啊三啊四
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:47.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A one and two and three and four
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.47,0:01:49.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多来几勺  冰淇淋不少
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:49.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need more scoops, ice cream galore
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.47,0:01:51.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然我就直接出门走人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.47,0:01:51.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or I'll banana split right out that door
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.55,0:01:54.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知不知道  我在奏高伯歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:54.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you know, I'm doing the Goober Rag
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.80,0:01:59.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱你  摇滚普斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:01:59.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love you, Rock T. Puss
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.95,0:02:02.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五啊六啊七啊八
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:02.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, five and six and seven and eight
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.40,0:02:04.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃完冰淇淋舔盘子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:04.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finish my ice cream, licking my plate
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.32,0:02:06.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来份软糖圣代挺不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:06.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another fudge sundae sure sounds great
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:07.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1016,798)}儿童税务
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.45,0:02:10.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就是高伯歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:10.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that is how I do that Goober Rag
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.25,0:02:14.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,九啊十啊十一十二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:14.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nine and ten and eleven and twelve
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.52,0:02:16.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,架上的朗姆葡萄干拿下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:16.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get the Rum Raisin off that shelf
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.25,0:02:18.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一整盒我自个吃光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:18.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll eat the whole tub all on my own
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.30,0:02:20.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连蛋筒我都用不着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:20.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I don't even need a cone
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.40,0:02:22.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知不知道  就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:22.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you know, that's how
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.40,0:02:24.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看清楚  我就在这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:24.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you see, I'm doing it now
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.17,0:02:25.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来了  又走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:25.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm coming, I'm going
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.14,0:02:28.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在奏高伯歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:28.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm doing the Goober Rag
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.03,0:02:37.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了小朋友  该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:37.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, boys, time to go
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.70,0:02:39.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能把我们踢出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:39.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't kick us out
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.10,0:02:42.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们打小就一直都来这了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:42.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've been coming here since we were kids
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.00,0:02:44.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  咱可是高菲掌勺乐队的头号粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:44.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're the Goofy Scoopers' biggest fans
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.96,0:02:46.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是你们自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:46.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's your problem
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.40,0:02:47.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都已经打烊了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:47.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Closing time
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.68,0:02:50.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可以不用回家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:50.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go home
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.07,0:02:51.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但就是不能待在这
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:51.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you can't stay here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.55,0:02:56.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒霉透了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:56.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This stinks
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.02,0:02:59.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来还想去后台要签名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.02,0:02:59.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanted to go backstage for an autograph
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:01.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1374,484)}海绵宝宝\N珊迪\N妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:01.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(764,656)}违停罚单
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:01.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1166,896)}痞老板到此一游
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别发愁了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.75,0:03:05.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们明天就能回来看高菲掌勺乐队了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:03.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll just come back
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:05.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and see the Goofy Scoopers tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:07.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1416,402)}法国旁白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:09.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}第二天早上
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.23,0:03:12.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:12.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.12,0:03:13.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我身上没钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:13.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't carry cash
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.16,0:03:16.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:16.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's you two
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.81,0:03:18.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们一整晚扎营蹲守在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:18.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We camped out all night
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.47,0:03:20.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要看高哎掌鞋乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:20.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to see the Gooey Sneakers
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高菲掌勺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goofy Scoopers
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.42,0:03:22.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:22.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, them
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们要往我头上签名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're gonna write on my head
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.66,0:03:25.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.66,0:03:25.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.80,0:03:27.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,关于乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:27.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about that
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.03,0:03:32.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高菲掌勺乐队结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:32.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Goofy Scoopers are over
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.72,0:03:34.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太过时了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:34.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too old fashioned
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.07,0:03:36.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友想要新的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:36.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The kids want a new sound
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.72,0:03:38.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:38.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A new sound?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.25,0:03:42.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我带来了能让你们兴奋的全新表演
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:42.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I brought in an act you're going to flip over
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.77,0:03:44.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:44.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say hello to
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.15,0:03:46.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,DJ两大勺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:46.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,DJ 2 Sc00pz
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.93,0:03:54.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  冰淇淋主题音乐机器人表演
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:54.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but the Goofy Scoopers are the only
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.37,0:03:57.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们只爱高菲掌勺乐队演的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:57.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ice cream themed musical robot act we'll ever love
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.52,0:04:04.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  别被嗡嗡呜呜的曲调迷住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:03.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, don't give in to its seductive
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:04.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,womp-womps and wub-wubs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.99,0:04:06.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了  经理先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:06.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, Mr. Manager
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.25,0:04:08.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快告诉我们掌勺乐队在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:08.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you have to tell us where the Scoopers are
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.40,0:04:10.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是在咖啡厅演出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:10.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are they playing at a coffee house?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是在裤头村碗演出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are they playing the Bikini Bottom Bowl?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.65,0:04:13.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是在世界巡演
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:13.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or on a world tour?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.48,0:04:17.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:17.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, no
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.34,0:04:19.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把那些老旧机器人扔垃圾堆了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:19.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I threw those old robots in the garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.82,0:04:23.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们再也不会演出了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:23.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're never playing anywhere again
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.77,0:04:33.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  你们把里面气氛都破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:33.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, you're killing the atmosphere in here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.67,0:04:35.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要哭就去外面哭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:35.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please do all your crying outside
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:45.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(394,186)}闲人免进
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.10,0:04:40.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:40.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.47,0:04:41.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:41.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a plan
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.47,0:04:43.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以不用哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:43.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can stop crying
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.17,0:04:44.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:44.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I wasn't crying
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.90,0:04:45.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:45.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.84,0:04:48.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿水冲我眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:48.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,flushing my eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were saying?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可以让高菲掌勺乐队复出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are gonna get the Goofy Scoopers back together
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上演重聚秀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for a reunion show
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.27,0:04:59.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后大家就都会铭记他们有多伟大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:59.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then everyone will remember how great they were
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.16,0:05:01.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可咱连他们在哪都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:01.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we don't know where they are
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.00,0:05:01.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:01.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,True
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.40,0:05:02.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过咱可是知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:02.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but we do know
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.35,0:05:07.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们是怎么抵达他们所在的去处的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:04.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how they got to where they were
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:07.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before they went wherever they are
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.89,0:05:12.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:12.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm confused
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.35,0:05:14.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我很欣赏你的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:14.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I appreciate your confidence
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Count me in
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:19.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}之后
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.11,0:05:30.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉卡车先借用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:30.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry about borrowing your truck
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们得去从垃圾堆那里救出机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have to save some robots from the trash
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.48,0:05:33.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我们最爱的乐队复出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:33.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so our favorite band can get back together
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.96,0:05:35.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定能体谅的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:35.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you understand
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.63,0:05:38.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,合情合理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:38.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sounds reasonable
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:42.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(790,264)}垃圾场
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.36,0:05:48.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们在对我的宝贝垃圾干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:48.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What you boys doing to my precious junk?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.00,0:05:48.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:48.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.99,0:05:51.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是在找几个机器乐手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:51.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just looking for some robot musicians
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在找吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I was looking for food
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.67,0:05:55.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要吃这根热狗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:55.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You gonna eat this hot dog?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.13,0:05:59.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我完全不懂什么乐手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:05:59.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know nothing about music-men
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.92,0:06:03.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我记得有个机器人来过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:03.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I do remember one robot fella coming through here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.85,0:06:05.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大好人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:05.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice guy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.10,0:06:07.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把他卖给了马戏团  赚了三块五
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:07.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sold him to the circus for about $3.50
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.51,0:06:09.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我们第一条线索有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:09.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, it's our first clue
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.35,0:06:10.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们得去马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:10.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We gotta get to the circus
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.87,0:06:13.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  因为我找到蛋黄酱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:13.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great, 'cause I just found the mayo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(808,542)}胶水
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.61,0:06:21.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在我宝贝垃圾场干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:21.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in my precious junkyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:24.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(840,458)}马戏团
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.47,0:06:26.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  是蛤蜊克莱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:26.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, it's Clem Clam
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get him
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.75,0:06:29.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:29.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,W-w-wait, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.29,0:06:30.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们来这是跟他交朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:30.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're here to make friends with him
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.57,0:06:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't you remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.09,0:06:33.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很明显我不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:33.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Obviously, I do not
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要怎么办才能让他演出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are we gonna get him to play the show?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.15,0:06:42.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以用合理论证跟有力论据让他理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:39.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll appeal to his intellect
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:42.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with sound reasoning and convincing arguments
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.29,0:06:43.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:43.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.92,0:06:46.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定要复出  一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:46.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You gotta come back, you just gotta
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别激动  爵士迷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can cool it, cats
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管你们计划是什么  我都加入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever your scheme is, I'm in
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.82,0:06:53.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我从这个疯狂马戏团里救出来就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:53.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just get me out of this crazy circus
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.35,0:06:55.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我特别怕小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:55.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm terrified of clowns, man
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.73,0:07:01.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就好  蛤蜊克莱先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:01.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's great, Mr. Clem Clam
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为明天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because tomorrow night
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.82,0:07:04.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要让乐团复出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:04.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're getting the band back together
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.70,0:07:07.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明晚在高菲高伯上演重聚秀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:07.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reunion show tomorrow night at Goofy Goober's
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.72,0:07:09.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过目前为止我只找到了你一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:09.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So far, you're the only one we've found, though
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.57,0:07:12.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全马戏团身体柔韧性最差的柔术演员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:12.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, the circus's least flexible contortionist
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.92,0:07:17.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在市中心那家按摩店看到了邦戈熊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:17.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,saw Bongos Bear at that massage place downtown, man
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.30,0:07:18.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:18.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's true--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.90,0:07:20.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:20.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.40,0:07:21.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:21.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,come on, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.45,0:07:23.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又有计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:23.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel another plan forming
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.52,0:07:25.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  带我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:25.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, take me with you, man
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:32.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034,474)}按摩
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.20,0:07:33.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:33.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.75,0:07:36.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟我老婆来这做夫妻按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:36.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my wife and I are here for the couples massage
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.23,0:07:38.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,话说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:38.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.05,0:07:40.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是高菲掌勺乐队那位邦戈熊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:40.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,aren't you Bongos Bear from the Goofy Scoopers?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.32,0:07:44.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你找错机器熊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:44.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Son, you got the wrong robot bear
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我连音乐都不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't even like music
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.02,0:07:48.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只做按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:48.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just give massages
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.46,0:07:51.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,屁股也得按摩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:51.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to work my glutes
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.23,0:08:08.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了好了  你们赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:08.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, all right, you win
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.07,0:08:10.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是邦戈熊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:10.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am Bongos Bear
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.00,0:08:13.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我冷冰冰的机器内心热爱音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:13.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I got music in my cold, robotic heart
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.23,0:08:15.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你可走运了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:15.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you're in luck
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.45,0:08:18.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟派大星要让你们乐队复出
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:16.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause Patrick and I
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:18.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are getting your band back together
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.50,0:08:21.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊  可我们还得找到钢琴章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:21.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but we still gotta find the piano octopus
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.11,0:08:23.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那简单
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:23.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's easy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.12,0:08:25.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个腰疼的建筑工人告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:25.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A construction worker with lumbago told me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.82,0:08:28.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摇滚现在在贝壳城的大桥工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:28.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rock is working on the bridge to Shell City now
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's true--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.42,0:08:32.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摇滚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:32.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rock?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.90,0:08:38.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摇滚普斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:38.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rock T. Puss?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.41,0:08:40.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:40.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This stinks
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.07,0:08:41.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邦戈骗了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:41.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bongos lied
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我根本没看到他在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't see him anywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.81,0:08:45.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点走开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:45.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.61,0:08:46.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在干活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:46.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on the job
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.89,0:08:48.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摇滚普斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:48.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rock T. Puss
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.52,0:08:50.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是海绵宝宝跟派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:50.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're SpongeBob and Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.02,0:08:51.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你的头号粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:51.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're your biggest fans
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.38,0:08:52.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:52.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.95,0:08:54.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没人记得我的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:54.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one remembers my music
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.38,0:08:55.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:55.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.62,0:08:57.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么都不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:57.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't remember anything
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.39,0:09:01.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听着  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:01.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, kids
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.05,0:09:02.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在是工程作业机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:02.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a working robot now
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.97,0:09:04.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我唯一关心的队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:04.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The only bands I care about
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.70,0:09:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有过桥的船只
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are the boats on this bridge
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.30,0:09:10.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船的鸣笛声才是我需要的掌声
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:08.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Their honking horns
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:10.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are the only applause I'll ever need again
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.42,0:09:14.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:14.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.85,0:09:16.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  都是热狗害的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:16.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I blame the hot dog
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了  普斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, Mr. Puss
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要让高菲掌勺乐队复出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're getting the Goofy Scoopers back together
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.71,0:09:21.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上演重聚秀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:21.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for a reunion show
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.95,0:09:23.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:23.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种事免谈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The answer is no
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.75,0:09:25.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在是座桥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:25.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a bridge now
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.58,0:09:26.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点走开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:26.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(838,560)}高菲高伯
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.24,0:09:33.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爵士迷们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.24,0:09:33.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, cats
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.18,0:09:34.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摇滚在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:34.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's Rock?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.88,0:09:35.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:35.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not coming
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.14,0:09:36.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:36.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.92,0:09:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没摇滚普斯  都不知道表演能不能成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know if we can do this without Rock T. Puss
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.30,0:09:42.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  我们跟你们一起演出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:42.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, we'll be playing with you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.55,0:09:43.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会很有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:43.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll be fun
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.94,0:09:45.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我写的新歌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:45.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's the new piece I wrote
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.92,0:09:47.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一开场就迅速进入状态
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:47.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're gonna come in hot off the intro
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽量跟上节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so try to keep up
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.02,0:09:56.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋  好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:56.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ice cream, so tasty
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.25,0:09:57.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰到嘴巴里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:57.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Freezing in my mouth
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.22,0:09:58.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脑子冻得特别疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:58.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Icy pain inside my brain
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Won't you help me out?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.35,0:10:01.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我大脑结冰  我大脑结冰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:01.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a brain freeze, I have a brain freeze
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我大脑结冰  快来救救我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a brain freeze, help me with my brain freeze
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能不能再来一份圣代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I have another sundae, please?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.35,0:10:14.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,观众全都不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:14.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They are not digging it, man
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.05,0:10:16.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都交代过你们要跟上节奏的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:16.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We told you guys to keep up
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.02,0:10:27.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摇滚普斯  你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:27.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rock T. Puss, you came
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.21,0:10:29.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:29.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry I left you hanging, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我确实喜欢当桥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did like being a bridge
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.37,0:10:34.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我生来就要创作音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:34.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I was built to make music
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.02,0:10:35.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,话说桥怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:35.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, how is the bridge?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.22,0:10:37.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:37.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure its fine
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.38,0:10:43.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起摇滚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:43.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, let's rock
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.19,0:10:56.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友还是不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:56.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The kids still don't like it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.51,0:10:57.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:57.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许我可以帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can help with that
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在下DJ两大勺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm DJ 2 Sc00pz
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.05,0:11:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是高菲掌勺乐队的铁粉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'm a huge Goofy Scoopers fan
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.60,0:11:06.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来狂欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:06.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Care to jam?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.57,0:11:37.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最棒的高菲掌勺乐队秀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:37.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Best Goofy Scoopers show ever
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:40.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(900,790)}本集完
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:42.63,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}派大狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:44.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(699.802,370)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:44.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(711.802,668)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:48.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:46.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(685.802,596)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(565.802,506)}联合监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:50.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(659.802,540)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:50.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:53.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(908,564)}动物收容所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:55.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1630,504)}办公室
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.40,0:11:56.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  动物管理局
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:56.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, animal control
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:12:08.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1308,860)}马文
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.86,0:12:00.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:00.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I appreciate you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.05,0:12:02.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来动物收容所做志愿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:02.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,volunteering here at the animal shelter
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.58,0:12:07.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你能不能别再让虫子用电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:04.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but could you please
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:07.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stop letting the worms use the phone?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.23,0:12:11.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我交代过它们不要再叫外卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:11.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told them no more takeout calls
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:14.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1256,756)}儿童餐
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.02,0:12:18.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  需要什么帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:18.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, how can I help you?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.12,0:12:21.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家外面有条虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.12,0:12:21.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a worm somewhere outside my house
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.08,0:12:22.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫个没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:22.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it won't stop barking
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这就过去处理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get on that right away
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.53,0:12:30.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得去抓流浪动物了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:30.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta go catch a stray
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.05,0:12:32.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你来帮我管收容所
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.05,0:12:32.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you hold down the fort
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.30,0:12:33.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:33.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sir, yes, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.42,0:12:36.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会尽力照顾好这些野虫子的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:35.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will take care of these wild worms
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:36.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the best of my ability
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:13:00.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(572,550)}刽子手
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,关刽子手的笼子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,B-B-Butcher's cage
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.10,0:13:09.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刽子手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:09.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Butcher?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.90,0:13:12.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你是个乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:12.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know you're really a good boy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.40,0:13:13.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我摸摸你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:13.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just let me pet you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.93,0:13:15.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轻轻摸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:15.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,real gentle
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That a boy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.42,0:13:23.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望它吃海绵还没吃习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:23.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope he doesn't develop a taste for sponge
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1226,486)}动物收容所
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.15,0:13:52.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:52.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.52,0:13:53.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:53.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's a good boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.64,0:13:55.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:55.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's a good boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星是我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick's my friend
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.45,0:14:02.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有时候他不小心吃了虫粮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:02.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sometimes if he's eaten worm food by mistake
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.95,0:14:04.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就会切换成虫子模式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:04.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's goes into worm mode
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.87,0:14:07.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道会持续多长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:07.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no telling how long it'll last
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.07,0:14:10.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是他在几天之内没被训好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:10.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if he's not trained in a few days
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.37,0:14:11.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,达到可以被收养的标准
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:11.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so he can be adopted
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.57,0:14:13.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就必须要锁进笼子里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:13.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he'll have to be locked up
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.31,0:14:14.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟刽子手一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:14.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like Butcher
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.47,0:14:18.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:18.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会训好他的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll train him
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他已经会定点排便了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's already housebroken
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道他排了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew he was broken
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.02,0:14:27.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还以为能定点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:27.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought it was house
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.77,0:14:32.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:32.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.72,0:14:35.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每条乖虫子都要学会做训练动作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:35.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,every good worm needs to learn how to do tricks
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.50,0:14:38.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,学得好就可以奖励虫粮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:38.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then they get wormy treats as a reward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.17,0:14:39.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:39.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sit
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.70,0:14:45.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:45.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.52,0:14:46.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再试另外一个动作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:46.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's try another one
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.07,0:14:47.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,握手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:47.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shake
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.92,0:14:53.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,试试翻滚看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:53.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shall we try roll over?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.47,0:14:58.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:58.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, wait
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:04.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(748,344)}地铁
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.67,0:15:09.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,翻滚海星快车  准时到达
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:09.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rolling Star Express, right on time
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.80,0:15:17.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有条小虫该去洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:17.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know one wormy that needs a bath
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.20,0:15:21.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不洗澡  不洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:21.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no bath, no bath
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.91,0:15:23.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.91,0:15:23.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.80,0:15:26.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虫子之间要互相学习
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:26.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Worms learn from other worms
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.23,0:15:29.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它们可以教你学乖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:29.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They'll show you how to be a good boy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:39.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}一小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:46.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(786,686)}终点
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.20,0:15:54.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这条虫子危害巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:54.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This worm is a menace
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.42,0:15:56.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恐怕他只能锁在笼子里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:56.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid he'll have to be locked up
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.80,0:15:57.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟刽子手一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:57.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like Butcher
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.92,0:15:59.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求求你别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:15:59.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please don't do that
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.73,0:16:00.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来收养他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:00.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll adopt him
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来带他回家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take him home
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.05,0:16:03.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我来救他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:03.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll be my rescue
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.44,0:16:06.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会对他负起全部责任吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:06.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you'll take full responsibility for him?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.67,0:16:08.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:08.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I promise
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.96,0:16:10.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:10.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's good
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.17,0:16:12.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正我不是很想把他恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:12.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really didn't want to have to fix him, anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.60,0:16:16.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:16.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.02,0:16:17.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:17.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.89,0:16:18.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:18.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoa, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.57,0:16:19.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:19.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heel
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.99,0:16:21.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:21.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.15,0:16:24.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:24.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给你带了个玩伴回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I brought you a playmate
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.60,0:16:35.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:35.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.97,0:16:37.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:37.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, stop
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.82,0:17:01.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:01.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.70,0:17:05.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:05.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.87,0:17:06.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:06.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.88,0:17:09.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吵到你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:09.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Was the noise bothering you?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.19,0:17:15.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:15.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, heel
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jeez
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.46,0:17:28.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:28.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.99,0:17:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不稀罕你们开的什么破烂怪派对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:30.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't care what kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,weird and stupid parties you throw
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.80,0:17:35.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只要你让你宠物安静消停点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:35.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just asking that you keep your pet quiet
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am at my wit's end
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星又变成虫子模式了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick is in worm mode again
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.35,0:17:41.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可这回他失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:41.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But this time, he's out of control
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.84,0:17:43.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是条虫子都能训好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:43.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any worm can be tamed
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.85,0:17:46.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连派大星那样傻的都能训
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:46.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even one as dumb as Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.18,0:17:48.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他只是需要严格教导
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:48.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He just needs tough love
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.75,0:17:52.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会严格教导派大星吗  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:52.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you tough-love Patrick, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.27,0:17:53.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:53.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.69,0:17:57.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:57.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.87,0:18:00.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定是最强的训虫师了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:18:00.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet you're the best worm trainer ever
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.32,0:18:01.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:01.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.42,0:18:03.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朝我作揖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:03.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beg me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, sit
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.15,0:18:15.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可真是个上好训傻师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:15.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm a good idiot trainer
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.42,0:18:18.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然派大星是个傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:18.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And since Patrick's an idiot
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.50,0:18:20.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我这就去训练他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:20.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll train him
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.59,0:18:22.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你得先装死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:22.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But only if you play dead--
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.58,0:18:27.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续装下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:27.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And stay playing dead
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.56,0:18:29.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得去训练傻子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:29.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got an idiot to train
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.06,0:18:37.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先从简单的开始训起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:37.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll start with something simple
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:37.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(324,534)}训虫方法
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.02,0:18:39.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来教你尾随我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:39.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you how to heel
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.07,0:18:41.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乖乖听话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:41.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,be a good boy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.35,0:18:45.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:45.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heel--
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.02,0:18:45.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:45.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stop
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.80,0:18:46.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:46.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heel
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.36,0:18:54.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  都够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:54.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, that's it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:02.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1600,286)}呛呛欢迎你来到\N海草林
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.47,0:19:06.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:06.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have a nice life
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.90,0:19:14.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:14.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.65,0:19:15.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还在装死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:15.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm still playing dead
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.60,0:19:21.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,严格教导
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:21.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tough love
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.21,0:19:34.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个  我的爱叫小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:34.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This, my little barking friend
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.39,0:19:36.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是电击项圈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:36.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is a shock collar
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.10,0:19:41.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每次你一叫  我就会按按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:41.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whenever you bark, I'll push this button
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.62,0:19:45.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你轻轻地严厉电一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:45.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and give you a mild tough-love shock
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.62,0:19:52.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没反应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:52.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.19,0:19:56.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:56.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It must be broken
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.80,0:20:00.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:00.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.85,0:20:22.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还在装死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:22.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still playing dead
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.67,0:20:56.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:56.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.65,0:20:58.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:58.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob tells me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.05,0:21:00.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你用严格教导来训好了派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:21:00.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that you've trained Patrick using tough love
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.74,0:21:01.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:01.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.50,0:21:03.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他无药可救
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:03.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's impossible
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.00,0:21:04.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来要教他坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:04.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've tried to get him to sit--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.15,0:21:11.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  然后我教他站起来作揖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:11.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, well, then I tried to get him to beg--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.17,0:21:14.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,转圈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:14.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spin
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.76,0:21:16.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,握手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:16.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now shake
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.31,0:21:20.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啦啦队式劈叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:20.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheerleader split
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.67,0:21:22.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,变成鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:22.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chicken
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.08,0:21:24.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,变成鸡块
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:24.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chicken nugget
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.66,0:21:25.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假装弹吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:25.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Air guitar
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.25,0:21:34.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在装死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:34.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now play dead
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.35,0:21:36.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:36.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.34,0:21:37.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:37.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.65,0:21:39.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你创造了奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:39.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a miracle worker
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.67,0:21:42.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是我吹牛  这可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:42.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't like to brag, but--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.40,0:21:43.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:43.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's great
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.62,0:21:46.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有条特别麻烦的虫子需要你来训
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:46.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got a problem worm that needs training
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.15,0:21:47.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:47.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.11,0:21:48.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家把它带进来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:48.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring him in, fellas
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:50.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,596)}动物管理局
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.02,0:21:54.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位就是刽子手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:54.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say hello to Butcher
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.47,0:22:00.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟上  跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.47,0:22:00.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heel, heel
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.49,0:22:01.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.49,0:22:01.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop--
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.05,0:22:02.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟上  跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.05,0:22:02.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,heel, heel--
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.61,0:22:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去捡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.61,0:22:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fetch
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.17,0:22:04.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟上  跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:04.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,heel, heel
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.14,0:22:06.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是虫子了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.14,0:22:06.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not a worm anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.90,0:22:10.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我几小时前就恢复原状了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:10.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nah, I snapped out of it hours ago
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.22,0:22:11.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是想让章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:11.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just wanted Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.72,0:22:13.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自我感觉良好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.72,0:22:13.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to feel like he did a good job
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.43,0:22:14.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  都够了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:14.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, that's enough
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.85,0:22:15.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要给你来点教训
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:15.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.57,0:22:17.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊  希望章鱼哥没对它太严了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.57,0:22:17.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I hope Squidward's not too tough on him
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.92,0:22:18.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐不坐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:18.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you sit?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.25,0:22:19.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:19.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.35,0:22:21.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下午好  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.35,0:22:21.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, gentlemen
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.94,0:22:23.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好个散步遛狗的好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:23.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice day for a walk
